{
  "stem": "7455.7",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the German personnel there went to a bunker to hide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were still sitting, peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the bullets were flying and bombs exploding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somebody said-- one of the girls said, then there is, from the general staff that's there, there's one, he called Richter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wants to get a girl to send to his parents-- a German girl.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They couldn't get any help in the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He lives near Cologne.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And perhaps I would go-- I would go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were rounding-- and he would include me in a Polish transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were rounding up girls to go to labor to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They could include me in that transport to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I wanted to be on that territory because if my brothers have survive, and the Russians come forward, then I can unite with my brothers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if they're alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I go to Germany, I'm distancing myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To me, Russia is now my liberator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If the Germans retreat, and I'm remained in that territory, I'll find out about my brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't want to go away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was impossible because it was the front line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The bombs and air raids and machine gunning and artillery-- I wouldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was not feeling good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had pain, so it would have been better for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm going to die here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I figure, if I survive the war, we had an uncle in Switzerland, which is a neutral country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the war, through him, we will find each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If my brothers survive, we'll find him, and I must go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I should go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In Germany, they don't know me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm a Polish Christian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to see this Herr Richter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was high ranking.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
